# Western Cape project location SEO

When editing Damtech project data or project images:

- Prefer a **Western Cape town/area**, not province-only labels ("Western Cape").
- Public SEO copy must name **both** the town and the province, e.g. "Tulbagh in the Western Cape".
- Image filenames and alt text should include **town + western-cape**.
- Do not change confirmed towns (Stellenbosch, Grabouw, etc.).

## Assigned WC market towns (previously unallocated)

| Town | Project slug | Image prefix |
|------|--------------|--------------|
| Tulbagh | `tulbagh-steel-water-tank` | `tulbagh-western-cape-steel-water-tank-*` |
| Worcester | `worcester-bitumen-earth-dam-lining-15000m2` | `worcester-western-cape-bitumen-earth-dam-*` |
| Villiersdorp | `villiersdorp-hdpe-dam-lining-8230m2` | `villiersdorp-western-cape-hdpe-dam-*` |

See also the convention comments at the top of `lib/projects.ts` and `lib/images.ts`.
